      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Distorted Zone would indeed make a good hideout. Could it mean that <FONT color=#a82424>Twisted Spring</FONT> where you first found signs of Grele is actually his base?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="QW_110.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-" mid="45" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Why don't you go back to <FONT color=#a82424>Twisted Spring</FONT> and look for <FONT color=#a82424>Grele</FONT> again? If Twisted Spring is his base, he would go back sooner or later even if he was away for a while.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-a" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>So irritating. Die, all of you!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-b" mid="47" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Relax, Grele! Don't you recognise me? It's me! {user_nick}!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-c" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Er… <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>…?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Grele squints and makes eye contact with you.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-d" mid="49" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>What are you doing at a place like this…? <BR>I was looking for my sister... She's the only family I have left now... These devices somewhat felt like hers so I was investigating them…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-d" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-e" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>So you were looking for </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Hiver</FONT><FONT color=#662500>'s body indeed.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-f" mid="51" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>…Her body? What are you talking about? She's still alive! She's not dead!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-g" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>There's something wrong with me now and I have terrible headaches from time to time. So I <FONT color=#a82424>swallowed a few jewels</FONT> and that made my head hurt again but I survived! Because... because my sister is still alive! Because I need to find her!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-h" mid="53" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Grele, I'm sorry to say that Hiver is dead and her body has already been buried. How can she come back to life again?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-i" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Hahahaha! <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you're a fool! Do you think getting buried would also kill the soul? That's not what's important! If the <FONT color=#a82424>seed</FONT> hasn't been destroyed... If the soul is alive…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-j" mid="55" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What do you mean? Grele, do you know something?!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-2" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>…….<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Grele suddenly keeps quiet.)</FONT><BR>I want to trust you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. But from my memory, I remember that you're <FONT color=#a82424>from Lagendia</FONT>. So if I tell you the truth, you'll become my enemy.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-1-" mid="58" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator Anser$<BR>………………….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2027_fountain_grele-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2027_fountain_grele-2-" mid="59" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I'll become his enemy? What is he talking about?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-a" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator Anser$<BR>I told you to stay away but why are you here?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Anser somehow looks nervous.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-b" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Did he chase after Grele all the way here? Grele's in danger!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-c" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What are YOU doing here? If you're after the thief, I didn't see him anywhere here….</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-d" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator Anser$<BR>That's because you're an insect whose eyes are good for nothing. I'm here because I saw his bright blue hair.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-e" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Did he see Grele with his own eyes? What should I do... Buy time?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-3" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator Anser$<BR>Nevermind. I don't have time to chat with you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2028_fountain_answer-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_answer.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2028_fountain_answer-3-" mid="66" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator Anser$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Anser quickly turns around and disappears.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
