      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>According to what you said, Grele has eaten up a few more jewels after killing Tryan so a low Child investigator would be a piece of cake to him. But things would become difficult if rumours about Grele spreads.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
